{
  "info": {
    "name": "Marketplace API — Payment",
    "_postman_id": "marketplace-api-v2-07-payment",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "order_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "payment_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "invoice_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "xendit_secret_key",
      "value": "xnd_development_YOUR_KEY_HERE",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "07. Payment",
      "description": "Module 7 — Payment: gateway charges, wallet, and refunds",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Payment",
          "description": "Initiate & manage payments via Xendit Invoice / Midtrans Snap",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Initiate Payment 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('payment_id', String(body.data.id || ''));",
                      "  const invoiceId = body.data.payment_details?.invoice_id || '';",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('invoice_id', invoiceId);",
                      "  pm.test('Initiate payment returns 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                      "  pm.test('Response has payment data', () => {",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('id');",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('status');",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('amount_cents');",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('redirect_url');",
                      "  });",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "X-Idempotency-Key",
                    "value": "{{$guid}}",
                    "description": "Unique key per request — prevents double payment"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"order_id\": {{order_id}},\n  \"gateway\": \"xendit\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/initiate",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "payments",
                    "initiate"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Buat gateway charge dan Payment record.\n\n**Selalu sertakan `X-Idempotency-Key`** (UUID) untuk mencegah double charge.\n\n**gateway** options:\n- `xendit` → Xendit Invoice hosted checkout (VA, QRIS, e-wallet, card semua tersedia di halaman invoice)\n- `midtrans` → Midtrans Snap hosted checkout\n\nMethod diassign otomatis oleh server: `xendit` → `invoice`, `midtrans` → `snap`.\n\nUser akan diarahkan ke `redirect_url` untuk menyelesaikan pembayaran. Webhook otomatis mengupdate status saat pembayaran selesai.\n\n`amount` stored as integer cents."
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "201 Created — Xendit Invoice",
                  "status": "Created",
                  "code": 201,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment initiated successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"invoice\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\",\n    \"payment_details\": {\n      \"external_id\": \"PAY-ABCDEFGHIJ-5\",\n      \"invoice_id\": \"623fca...\",\n      \"invoice_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\"\n    },\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "201 Created — Midtrans Snap",
                  "status": "Created",
                  "code": 201,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment initiated successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"order_id\": 6,\n    \"gateway\": \"midtrans\",\n    \"method\": \"snap\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/v4/redirection/...\",\n    \"payment_details\": {\n      \"snap_token\": \"abc123...\",\n      \"redirect_url\": \"https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/v4/redirection/...\"\n    },\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "201 Created — Existing Pending Payment Returned",
                  "status": "Created",
                  "code": 201,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment initiated successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"invoice\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\",\n    \"payment_details\": { \"invoice_id\": \"623fca...\", \"invoice_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\" },\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "422 Unprocessable — Order Not Owned",
                  "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
                  "code": 422,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"The given data was invalid.\",\n  \"errors\": {\n    \"order_id\": [\"The selected order id is invalid.\"]\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Get Payment Status 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Get status returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                      "pm.test('Response has status field', () => {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('status');",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('amount_cents');",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/{{payment_id}}/status",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "payments",
                    "{{payment_id}}",
                    "status"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Poll status pembayaran. Frontend menggunakan ini untuk mendeteksi saat pembayaran Invoice/Snap selesai.\n\nReturns Payment dengan relasi order dan transaction."
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK — Pending",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment status retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"invoice\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\",\n    \"payment_details\": { \"invoice_id\": \"623fca...\", \"invoice_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\" },\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "200 OK — Paid",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment status retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"xendit\",\n    \"method\": \"invoice\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"paid\",\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://checkout.xendit.co/v2/623fca...\",\n    \"payment_details\": { \"invoice_id\": \"623fca...\" },\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Switch Payment Gateway 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('payment_id', String(body.data.id || ''));",
                      "  const invoiceId = body.data.payment_details?.invoice_id || '';",
                      "  pm.collectionVariables.set('invoice_id', invoiceId);",
                      "  pm.test('Switch returns 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                      "  pm.test('New payment created', () => {",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('id');",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data.status).to.equal('pending');",
                      "    pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('redirect_url');",
                      "  });",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
                  { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"gateway\": \"midtrans\"\n}",
                  "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/{{payment_id}}/switch",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "payments", "{{payment_id}}", "switch"]
                },
                "description": "Ganti gateway pembayaran untuk payment yang sedang **pending**.\n\nMekanisme:\n1. Expire invoice/snap lama di gateway (best-effort — tidak gagal jika sudah expire)\n2. Payment lama → status `expired`\n3. Buat gateway charge baru dengan gateway yang diminta\n4. Return Payment baru dengan `redirect_url` baru\n\n**Order tidak dibatalkan** — tetap `pending` sampai timer habis.\n\n**Hanya bekerja untuk payment berstatus `pending`.** Paid/expired/refunded → 422."
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "201 Created — Switched to Midtrans",
                  "status": "Created",
                  "code": 201,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Payment method switched.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 2,\n    \"order_id\": 5,\n    \"gateway\": \"midtrans\",\n    \"method\": \"snap\",\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"redirect_url\": \"https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/v4/redirection/...\",\n    \"payment_details\": {\n      \"snap_token\": \"abc123...\",\n      \"redirect_url\": \"https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/v4/redirection/...\"\n    },\n    \"expires_at\": \"2026-05-13T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:01:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:01:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "422 Unprocessable — Payment Not Pending",
                  "status": "Unprocessable Entity",
                  "code": 422,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Can only switch a pending payment.\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "404 Not Found — Wrong User",
                  "status": "Not Found",
                  "code": 404,
                  "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"No query results for model [App\\\\Models\\\\Payment].\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Request Refund 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Refund returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                      "pm.test('Refund has id', () => {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('id');",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data.status).to.equal('processed');",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"reason\": \"Item not received\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/payments/{{payment_id}}/refund",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "payments",
                    "{{payment_id}}",
                    "refund"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Request refund untuk payment milik user yang terautentikasi.\n\n- **Paid**: gateway refundPayment() + create Refund record + Payment status → refunded\n- **Pending/Expired**: cancel only — no gateway call, Payment status → failed\n\nHanya buyer pemilik order yang dapat request refund."
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Refund processed successfully.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"payment_id\": 1,\n    \"amount_cents\": 39000000,\n    \"amount\": \"Rp 390.000\",\n    \"reason\": \"Item not received\",\n    \"status\": \"processed\",\n    \"refunded_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                },
                {
                  "name": "404 Not Found — Wrong User",
                  "status": "Not Found",
                  "code": 404,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"No query results for model [App\\\\Models\\\\Payment].\",\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Wallet",
          "description": "Wallet balance, transactions, top-up and merchant withdrawal",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Get Wallet Balance 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Balance returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                      "pm.test('Response has balance fields', () => {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('balance_cents');",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('available_cents');",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data).to.have.property('on_hold_cents');",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/balance",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "wallet",
                    "balance"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Ambil saldo wallet user yang terautentikasi.\n\nWallet dibuat otomatis (`firstOrCreate`) saat pertama kali diakses — tidak perlu inisialisasi manual.\n\n`available_cents = balance_cents - on_hold_cents`"
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Wallet balance retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"balance_cents\": 50000000,\n    \"balance\": \"Rp 500.000\",\n    \"on_hold_cents\": 10000000,\n    \"on_hold\": \"Rp 100.000\",\n    \"available_cents\": 40000000,\n    \"available\": \"Rp 400.000\"\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "List Wallet Transactions 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Transactions returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                      "pm.test('Response has pagination', () => {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.expect(body.meta).to.have.property('pagination');",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/transactions?page=1",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "wallet",
                    "transactions"
                  ],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "page",
                      "value": "1"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Riwayat transaksi wallet user (paginated, 20 per page, latest first).\n\n`type`: `credit` (masuk) atau `debit` (keluar)"
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Wallet transactions retrieved.\",\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 2,\n      \"type\": \"credit\",\n      \"amount_cents\": 50000000,\n      \"amount\": \"Rp 500.000\",\n      \"description\": \"Top-up via Xendit Invoice\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"type\": \"debit\",\n      \"amount_cents\": 10000000,\n      \"amount\": \"Rp 100.000\",\n      \"description\": \"Withdrawal — on_hold\",\n      \"created_at\": \"2026-05-12T09:00:00.000000Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\",\n    \"pagination\": { \"current_page\": 1, \"last_page\": 1, \"per_page\": 20, \"total\": 2 }\n  }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Topup Wallet 🔒",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"amount\": 50000000\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/wallet/topup",
                  "host": [
                    "{{base_url}}"
                  ],
                  "path": [
                    "api",
                    "wallet",
                    "topup"
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Initiate wallet top-up via payment gateway.\n\nAlur: POST ini mengembalikan instruksi untuk melanjutkan ke `POST /api/payments/initiate` dengan jumlah yang sama. Kredit wallet terjadi otomatis via `PaymentCaptured` → `CreditUserWallet` listener setelah pembayaran berhasil.\n\n`amount` dalam integer cents. Min: Rp 10.000 (1000000 cents)."
              },
              "response": [
                {
                  "name": "200 OK",
                  "status": "OK",
                  "code": 200,
                  "header": [
                    {
                      "key": "Content-Type",
                      "value": "application/json"
                    }
                  ],
                  "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Top-up payment initiated. Complete payment to credit wallet.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"message\": \"Redirect user to initiate a payment via POST /api/payments/initiate with the wallet top-up amount.\",\n    \"amount\": 50000000\n  },\n  \"meta\": { \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-12T10:00:00.000000Z\" }\n}"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "name": "Withdraw (Merchant Only) 🔒",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "pm.test('Withdraw returns 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                      "pm.test('on_hold increased', () => {",
                      "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                      "  pm.expect(body.data.on_hold_cents).to.be.greaterThan(0);",
                      "});"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Accept",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  },
